{"id": "1278094392795729960", "channel_id": "1278094392795729960", "type": 0, "author_id": "372020544494764043", "author_name": "ariate", "author_bot": false, "content": "如題，這樣我不敢用。", "timestamp": "2024-08-27T20:50:49.088000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1278094392959303792", "filename": "Screenshot_20240827_214921__Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 105552, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1278094392795729960/1278094392959303792/Screenshot_20240827_214921__Morimens.jpg?ex=69cc33a9&is=69cae229&hm=71e5110656de4952002e46e0ced6d25f9f8502b9c137275129b8a0c066206add&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278094392795729960", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」相位希洛卡顯示問題", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1277976752622407680", "channel_id": "1277976752622407680", "type": 0, "author_id": "369053445761662976", "author_name": "sallyfishdestine", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為我沒有拿到禮帽的時候都是抽牌正常的\n但有拿到禮帽之後\n在即為罕見的情況下，也就是把牌庫抽乾\n（因為我這邊有「眼」所以辦得到）\n會發現所有會抽牌的牌或是技能\n原本會把棄牌堆中的牌放回去重抽的都再也抽不到牌了\nhttps://youtu.be/fgPdC9-aPHI\n影片中不管是靈感還是萊克的技能都抽不到牌了\n（上半段問題已解決）\n題外話，如附圖\n嚴格來說不算BUG，但我覺得是設計上的BUG\n是號令在牌庫被改成2費之後再抽入手被帽子改成4費\n但是很奇怪啊，因為號令減費效果之前說是「光環效果」\n也就是說無時無刻生效\n但我的這張卡不會變成6費啊\n所以我怎麼可能會有4費的號令呢？\n\n以上報告。", "timestamp": "2024-08-27T13:03:21.485000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-27T13:54:01.780000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1277976752790048821", "filename": "20240827_BUG.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 163834, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1277976752622407680/1277976752790048821/20240827_BUG.jpg?ex=69cbc619&is=69ca7499&hm=0959f3b16d8bec0cc0965ee2f1744af229ffec2bf671ff518c1efec5ebb684c6&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "20240827 詭術禮帽沒有抽牌的BUG", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fgPdC9-aPHI", "description": ""}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1277976752622407680", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "估計是詭術禮帽的BUG（部分已解決）", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
